Package: RClinVarbitration
Type: Package
Title: Stream ClinVar XML into DuckDB Semantic Graphs
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "Sounkou Mahamane", family = "Toure",
           email = "sounkoutoure@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person(given = "DuckDB Foundation", role = "cph",
           comment = "Bundled DuckDB C extension headers")
    )
Description: Streams official 'ClinVar' VCV XML releases, including gzip
    inputs, into a queryable semantic graph in 'DuckDB'. A package-owned native
    extension uses libxml2's forward reader and emits ordered XML element,
    attribute, and text statements; SQL materializes graph and discovery-text
    tables without loading the release into R. Versioned ClinVarbitration policy
    is a derived SQL layer over the retained source facts.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
